{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c633741f10","title":"有法可依、有法必依都没有完全做到","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"af0c02fc6d","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"c633741f10"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"2822a439cf","name":"戴逸樵"},{"id":"55d4e5b786","name":"中国人民大学"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"dd057d65b7","type":"title","text":"有法可依、有法必依都没有完全做到","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c633741f10"},{"id":"9738f0a472","type":"authors","text":"中国人民大学戴逸樵","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c633741f10"},{"id":"a313888ba0","type":"subtitle","text":"（戴逸樵：中国人民大学法律系学生；摘录，标题为原编者所加）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c633741f10"},{"id":"37642d8716","type":"paragraph","text":"法制是意味着二方面：一方面有法可依，另一方面有法必依。在我国这二方面都没有完全做到，表现在：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c633741f10"},{"id":"f5ed5a84d1","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）无法可依：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c633741f10"},{"id":"7eb158d35c","type":"paragraph","text":"我国的宪法仅是原则性的东西，而我国没有民法典、刑法典、劳动法等等，因此判案大部分是按照党的政策及审判人员法的意识办事，伸缩性很大。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c633741f10"},{"id":"1c8000df31","type":"paragraph","text":"国务院，国务院所属各部、委，各省（市）根据宪法规定所颁布的条例、法令、法规等规范性文件，这是都不能算是法，认为只有最高权力机关颁布的规范性文件才是法。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c633741f10"},{"id":"362cd3b85f","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）有法不依：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c633741f10"},{"id":"c56145ad90","type":"paragraph","text":"1．有一地方，公安机关70多人，而检察机关3人，公安机关要逮捕人，检察院不批准不行，因此批准是形式。我们人民大学法律系都违反法制（搜身事件）何况其他地方，其他部门？","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c633741f10"},{"id":"d5bb584de1","type":"paragraph","text":"2．肃反运动中，检查肃反对象的信件，这是违反宪法的。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c633741f10"},{"id":"a38cff1b36","type":"paragraph","text":"3．肃反扩大化了，错杀了一个人就算是扩大化。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c633741f10"},{"id":"ef9cb1be74","type":"paragraph","text":"4．我国地方各级人民代表大会特别是基层人民代表大会，经常不按期召开。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c633741f10"},{"id":"5efee321bf","type":"paragraph","text":"5．搜身事件，学校、保卫科主观上就是违反法制。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c633741f10"},{"id":"185165787b","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《高等学校右派言论选编》（中共中国人民大学委员会，1958年8月）。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c633741f10"}],"page":{"id":"d5c33c8646","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c633741f10","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}